Package io.helidon.tracing.zipkin

Class ZipkinTracer

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.helidon.tracing.zipkin.ZipkinTracer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Tracer

    public class ZipkinTracer
extends Object
implements Tracer
    The ZipkinTracer delegates to BraveTracer while creating ZipkinSpanBuilder instead of BraveSpanBuilder. This class should not be sued directly, use either TracerBuilder or ZipkinTracerBuilder.
    See Also:
    Zipkin Attributes, Zipkin Missing Service Name, ZipkinSpanBuilder
